ications with law enforcement or regulators such as the CFTC. The provision=
s caused confusion that resulted in an impediment to voluntary and direct c=
ommunications with the CFTC about possible violations of the [Commodity Exc=
hange Act] and CFTC regulations in violation of the CEA=E2=80=99s prohibiti=
ons against impeding direct communications with the CFTC.</p></blockquote><=
